column2: "Hey, baby! Come on, over here!"
"H-hey! Wait up!"
"Haaa, haaa, if we come this far we should be okay right?"
"Just because we stepped on it a little doesn't mean it should get so angry."
"That's normal to be angry!"
"Oh hey, it's you."
"Hey listen up, you wouldn't believe how much of a rookie this girl is!"
"She even managed to somehow step on a sleeping enemy. I couldn't believe my eyes!"
"Hey, shut up! It worked out didn't it?"
"I'd rather not have something like that ever happen again."
"You're one to talk. You're so spineless that you run away at the drop of a pin."
"Not to mention that the one who talked to us first was you. Weren't you scared then?"
"We are from a different planet after all."
"Coming from a different planet doesn't make too much difference."
"Recently really scary guys just started appearing out of nowhere."
"And the enemies here weren't always this strong."
"All of a sudden, they got really violent can't understand words. It was really troublesome."
"So at least my words get across to you. That much is a lot better."
"But there are always exceptions."
"... Do you have a death wish?"
